# 📘 HRMS PRODUCTION BLUEPRINT (FOR CODEX)

## 🎯 OBJECTIVE
Build a production-ready multi-tenant HRMS system using:
- Backend: Java Spring Boot
- Frontend: React (Vite + Tailwind)
- Database: MySQL
- Auth: JWT + Refresh Token

---

# 🧠 SYSTEM RULES (STRICT)

- Follow layered architecture:
  Controller → Service → Repository → DB
- Use DTO for all APIs
- Use global exception handling
- All tables MUST include `company_id` (multi-tenant)
- Use standard API response:
  { success, message, data, meta }
- Use REST API prefix: `/api/v1`
- Use role-based access control (RBAC)

---

# 🧩 MODULES (BUILD IN ORDER)

## 1. AUTH MODULE (PRIORITY 1)
Features:
- Register Company
- Login (email + password + company_code)
- JWT + Refresh Token
- Forgot Password (OTP)
- Logout

APIs:
- POST /auth/register-company
- POST /auth/login
- POST /auth/refresh
- POST /auth/logout
- POST /auth/forgot-password
- POST /auth/reset-password
- GET  /auth/me

---

## 2. EMPLOYEE MODULE
Features:
- Employee CRUD
- Department
- Designation
- Employee Directory

APIs:
- GET /employees
- POST /employees
- GET /employees/{id}
- PUT /employees/{id}
- DELETE /employees/{id}
- GET /departments
- POST /departments
- GET /designations

---

## 3. ATTENDANCE MODULE
Features:
- Clock-in / Clock-out
- Working hours calculation
- Attendance status

APIs:
- POST /attendance/clock-in
- POST /attendance/clock-out
- GET /attendance
- GET /attendance/today
- PUT /attendance/{id}

---

## 4. LEAVE MODULE
Features:
- Leave types
- Leave balance
- Apply leave
- Approval workflow

APIs:
- GET /leave-types
- GET /leave/balance
- POST /leave/apply
- GET /leave/my-requests
- POST /leave/{id}/approve
- POST /leave/{id}/reject

---

## 5. PAYROLL MODULE
Features:
- Salary structure
- Payroll run
- Salary slip

APIs:
- POST /salary-structures
- POST /payroll/run
- GET /payroll/{month}/{year}
- GET /payroll/slip/{empId}/{month}/{year}

---

## 6. TASK MODULE
Features:
- Project
- Task assignment
- Task status
- Comments

APIs:
- POST /projects
- GET /projects
- POST /tasks
- GET /tasks
- PUT /tasks/{id}/status

---

## 7. OTHER MODULES
- Visits
- Meetings
- Files
- Notifications
- Analytics

